room_title: Escape room "Ariana's Wedding" by Lost Cruces Escape Room in Las Cruces
review: It was very challenging, but loads of fun! The kids did better than the adults! Awesome customer service and friendly, supportive atmosphere. Amazing attention to detail.

room_title: Escape room "Ariana's Wedding" by Lost Cruces Escape Room in Las Cruces
review: It was a wonderful time. Took the kids, 11 and 6, they figured out more than adults . Staff was great and fun. We will definitely do it again. What a unique way to spend and evening. Well worth it.
